data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom home is a true gem in the highly sought after Barrington Chase Subdivision. With a host of impressive features, including a partially finished basement, main floor owner's suite, and a captivating pool, this home offers the ultimate in luxury living! Recent renovations to the basement have elevated the property to new heights! The in-ground pool expertly installed by Brown's Pools and recently relined, promises refreshing relief during the sweltering summer months. An entertainer's dream! Step inside the welcoming foyer, where hardwood flooring sets the tone for elegance throughout. The kitchen is perfect for the chef in you boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample space for culinary creations. The main floor owner's suite is a sanctuary unto itself, featuring a trey ceiling, a spacious walk-in closet, separate vanities, a separate shower, and a luxurious jetted tub. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms await, along with a full bathroom featuring dual vanities. Descend to the partially finished upgraded basement, where you'll find an additional bedroom, full bathroom, family room/playroom equip with a kitchenette, storage room, and workshop perfect for accommodating guests or pursuing hobbies. With an exterior entrance, it could be a rental space for sure! Outside, the screened-in porch offers a serene spot to enjoy the picturesque backyard and pool, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and recreation alike. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this private oasis your own. WELCOME HOME!! NOTE: We have a recent APPRAISAL in hand.
